---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Chain Link Fence Installation - Affordable Fence & Railing, LLC"
  description="Maintenance-free chain link fencing in Pittsburgh, PA. Galvanized and black vinyl-coated options. Residential and commercial installations. Free estimates."
>
  <!-- Full-bleed sunset hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/images/gettyimages-928863520-1920w.jpg" alt="" class="hero-bg" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content wrap">
      <span class="label">Chain Link</span>
      <h1>Low Maintenance. High Durability.</h1>
      <p>Chain link fencing in a wide range of colors, heights, and styles. Gates available in sliding or swinging configurations.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Two options — side by side -->
  <section class="options section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2 class="reveal">Two Options, One Standard</h2>
      <div class="options-grid">
        <div class="option-card reveal">
          <div class="option-color galvanized"></div>
          <h3>Galvanized</h3>
          <p>The classic silver chain link. Galvanized coating protects against rust and corrosion. A cost-effective choice for property boundaries and security.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="option-card reveal">
          <div class="option-color vinyl-coated"></div>
          <h3>Black Vinyl-Coated</h3>
          <p>Vinyl-coated chain link blends into the landscape for a cleaner look. The coating adds an extra layer of weather protection. A popular upgrade for residential properties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="content section">
    <div class="wrap content-grid">
      <div class="content-text">
        <h2 class="reveal">Reliable Fencing for Every Property</h2>
        <p class="reveal">Chain link is one of the best maintenance-free options available. A galvanized residential chain link fence provides safety for animals and defines the line of your property.</p>
        <p class="reveal">We provide competitively priced, customized installations for residential properties. Commercial and residential customers will be impressed with our quality galvanized chain link fences.</p>
        <p class="reveal">Chain link is ideal for pool enclosures, privacy fences, dog kennel fences, tennis court fences, and overall security. We also install gates that can slide or swing open for access.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-image reveal">
        <img src="/images/img_2035-640w-1920w.webp" alt="Black vinyl chain link fence" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits — horizontal scrolling cards -->
  <section class="benefits section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2 class="reveal">Why Chain Link</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-scroll">
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <span class="benefit-num">01</span>
        <h3>Budget Friendly</h3>
        <p>One of the most affordable fencing options on the market.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <span class="benefit-num">02</span>
        <h3>Zero Maintenance</h3>
        <p>No painting, staining, or sealing required. Ever.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <span class="benefit-num">03</span>
        <h3>Fast Installation</h3>
        <p>Our team gets your fence up with minimal disruption.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <span class="benefit-num">04</span>
        <h3>Durable</h3>
        <p>Built to last through Pittsburgh weather, year after year.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <span class="benefit-num">05</span>
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p>Reliable protection for pets, children, and property.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <span class="benefit-num">06</span>
        <h3>Easy Repair</h3>
        <p>Individual sections can be fixed without replacing the whole fence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta section">
    <div class="wrap cta-inner">
      <h2>Get a Chain Link Fence Estimate</h2>
      <p>Call us today to find out if chain link is right for your home.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Free Estimate</a>
        <a href="tel:412-766-1464" class="btn btn-outline">Call 412-766-1464</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero with golden hour chain link photo */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 65vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      oklch(0.14 0.005 260 / 0.85) 0%,
      oklch(0.14 0.005 260 / 0.3) 100%
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    padding-block: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero h1 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .hero p { color: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.7); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); max-width: 42ch; }

  /* Options cards */
  .options h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .options-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .options-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  .option-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid oklch(0 0 0 / 0.06);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .option-color {
    width: 100%;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .galvanized { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #b8b8b8, #d4d4d4, #a8a8a8); }
  .vinyl-coated { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a1a1a, #333, #1a1a1a); }

  .option-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .option-card p { color: var(--steel); font-size: 0.9375rem; }

  /* Content */
  .content { background: var(--cream-dark); }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  .content-text h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .content-text p { color: var(--steel); }

  .content-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  }

  /* Benefits — horizontal scrolling */
  .benefits {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    background-image: var(--picket-pattern);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .benefits h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .benefits-scroll {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (max-width: 959px) {
    .benefits-scroll {
      padding-inline: var(--gutter);
    }
  }

  .benefit-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--iron);
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .benefit-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.08);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    color: var(--silver);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    background: var(--teal);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-inner { max-width: 600px; }
  .cta h2 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .cta p { color: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.75); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
</style>
